<st-form-item
  :class="b()"
  :labelGutter="labelGutter"
  :labelWidth="labelWidth"
  :required="required"
>
  <template slot="label">
    <slot v-if="$slots.label" name="label"></slot>
    <template>{{ label }}</template>
  </template>
  <a-radio-group
    v-model="currentType"
    :options="types"
    :disabled="disabled"
    @change="onTypeChange"
  ></a-radio-group>
  <st-container
    v-show="isShowShopList"
    class="mg-t16"
    :class="b('container')"
  >
    <a-checkbox-group
      v-decorator="decorators.currentShopIds"
      :disabled="disabled"
      @change="onShopIdsChange"
      class="full-width"
    >
      <a-row>
        <a-col
          :span="12"
          v-for="item in shopList"
          :key="item.value"
          :class="b('item')"
        >
          <a-checkbox :value="item.id">{{ item.shop_name }}</a-checkbox>
        </a-col>
      </a-row>
    </a-checkbox-group>
  </st-container>
</st-form-item>
